Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:57.09,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{couldn't pull it off?}cũng không thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.46,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{No fucking way.}Đùa nhau à...
