Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:31.63,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{I-I think... you're... Instructor Kato... \Nthe teacher, right?}Là ông... à... thầy Kato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:37.64,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{I doubt you... remember me, but...}Chắc ông không nhớ tôi đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.14,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{I saw something...}Tôi đã thấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:47.23,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{When I became a nukenin... \Nand made contact with UN...}Khi trở thành ninja lưu lạc... tôi đã liên hệ với UN...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:51.19,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{Gonna keep killing until the day I die!}Tôi sẽ giết đến ngày mình chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.86,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{I saw... something...}Tôi đã thấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:00.98,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{Behind the graves... It was him...}Phía sau ngôi mộ... là hắn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:06.83,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{The disguise... of Commander Sasama!}Chỉ huy... Sasama cải trang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.85,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Hachiya-kun... Kato...}Hachiya... Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.33,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Here it comes.}Nó đến đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:32.61,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,Nó đến rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.86,Flashback,Saruta,0,0,0,,{more chaos—}sự hỗn loạn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.10,Flashback,Male Student 1,0,0,0,,{Will you go out with me?}Hẹn hò với tớ nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:51.88,Flashback,Girl Student 2,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:00.75,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Ahoy-hoy. We've got work to do.}Đến lượt chúng ta rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.88,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Huh? It's just a way of saying hello.}Hả? Chỉ là chào hỏi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.52,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Contact the governor and have him \Nset up a disaster response task force.}Liên hệ với tổng bộ yêu cầu\N thành lập nhóm ứng phó thảm hoạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.66,Flashback,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,{Wh-What the...}G-Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.89,Flashback,Fattytake,0,0,0,,{S-Sensei!}T-Thầy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.96,Flashback,Head Teacher,0,0,0,,{Fattytake—}Mập--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:17.65,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{You'll wanna use script A-22 for the media, \Ncops, and fire department.}Cậu sẽ sử dụng lệnh A-22 cho giới truyền thông, \Ncảnh sát và sở cứu hoả.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:23.41,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Stick to the plan. \NSay the explosion was caused}Theo kế hoạch, vụ nổ đã xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:26.79,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{by a massive buildup of \Nmethane gas in the sewers.}Nguyên nhân là khí metan tích tụ trong cống.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:36.55,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{The physical cordon of the \Narea around Kodan High School}Phong toả xung quanh cao trung Kodan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:39.00,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{and info control take top priority.}và ưu tiên kiểm soát thông tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.37,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Business as usual, wrapped up tidy.}Công việc dọn dẹp như mọi khi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:44.30,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Huh? You know, "wrap it up," like finish it.}Hả? Dọn dẹp hậu cuộc ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.39,Flashback,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Man, you don't have a clue, do you?}Cậu không hiểu gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.25,Default,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Sato, come on!}Sato, mau lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:14.96,Default,Sato,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:17.96,Default,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{This is an important part. \NMake sure to get it.}Đây là phần quan trọng nhất đó, chụp đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.97,Default,Sato,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:23.59,Default,Noguchi,0,0,0,,{Could you please hurry up? This is hard!}Làm ơn nhanh lên đi, nặng quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.25,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{That explosion...}Vụ nổ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.34,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Is that what Kuro-san was talking about?}Là thứ Kuro nói à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.65,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Yamada-san! Your nose! \NWhat happened to your nose?!}Yamada! Mũi cậu! Mũi cậu đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.31,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{I-It's gone!}N-Nó mất rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.57,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Y-You okay?}C-Cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:45.27,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{D-Do you have... a head in your hands?}T-Tay cậu... cái đầu đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.32,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{A human head?!}Đầu người?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:17.23,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Did I just kick...}Thứ mình vừa đá...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.98,Default,Ranran,0,0,0,,{Manager Taira.}Quản lý Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:27.38,Default,Ranran,0,0,0,,{You're sweating bullets. You gonna be okay?}Anh toát mồ hôi ghê thế? Ổn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.12,Default,Ranran,0,0,0,,{So, what happened with Escape?}Thế chuyện gì đã xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:36.00,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{Escape's orbit is decaying. \NIt's on course for atmospheric re-entry.}Quỹ đạo của Ecape đã lệch, \Nnó đang tiến vào bầu khí quyển.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.48,Default,Ranran,0,0,0,,{So it's totaled...}Vậy là...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:44.44,Default,Ranran,0,0,0,,{And UN has acquired NIN's personal data \Nfrom the server, haven't they?}UN đã lấy được dữ liệu \Ncá nhân của NIN từ máy chủ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.50,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{No...}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:52.26,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{There was no confirmation of any \Nlarge-bandwidth transmissions from Escape.}Không có xác nhận về bất kỳ \Nđường truyền băng thông lớn nào từ Escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.02,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{But there's a good chance a landing unit}Nhưng rất có khả năng đơn vị đổ bộ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:59.27,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{containing some kind of storage \Nmedium may have gotten away.}chứa dữ liệu lưu trữ đã trốn thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.40,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{The seven NIN leaders have assembled}Bảy thủ lĩnh NIN đã tập trung lại
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.51,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{at the Grand Ninja Command \Nto assume operational control.}tại tổng bộ Ninja để nắm quyền kiểm soát.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:12.30,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{That means NIN has officially \Ntransitioned to a war footing.}Điều đó có nghĩa là NIN đã phát động chiến tranh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.36,Default,7 Nin 1,0,0,0,,{Why did they drag us out here?}Sao tự nhiên lại gọi chúng ta ra đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.75,Default,7 Nin 2,0,0,0,,{They wanna wreck little Escape.}Họ muốn phá huỷ bé Escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:21.17,Default,7 Nin 3,0,0,0,,{Do just the five of us get to make the call?}Chỉ cần 5 người bấm nút thôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:25.13,Default,7 Nin 2,0,0,0,,{We sure can. It's a majority \Nvote among the seven of us.}Được mà, dù gì cũng chỉ có 7 người.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.43,Default,7 Nin 5,0,0,0,,{Five of us is a majority, all right.}Năm phiếu là thuận rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:34.55,Default,7 Ninja 3,0,0,0,,{Uh, which button was it again?}Nút nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:39.44,Default,7 Nin 4,0,0,0,,{The red one! Have you really forgotten that?}Màu đỏ! Bà lại quên nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:43.06,Default,7 Nin 2,0,0,0,,{Do you think Tara-chan's gotten any bigger?}Tara-chan không biết lớn chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:47.82,Default,7 Nin 3,0,0,0,,{He's still a baby. \NCan't even talk yet, I hear.}Vẫn còn nhỏ lắm, chưa nói được luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.95,Default,7 Nin 4,0,0,0,,{I can't wait to be young again, too.}Tôi cũng muốn mau chóng trẻ lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:55.08,Default,7 Nin 2,0,0,0,,{Hopefully before we die.}Hi vọng chờ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:13.46,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{The loss of Escape means losing \Nour decisive advantage over UN...}Mất đi Escape đồng nghĩa với\N việc mất đi lợi thế trước UN...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:20.09,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{With the potential loss of the personal data,}Với nguy cơ mất thông tin cá nhân,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:22.23,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{anyone above chunin will be\N brought in for the response,}bất kì ai ở cấp cao hơn chunin đều sẽ bị triệu tập.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:26.23,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{forcing all of them to abandon \Ntheir current missions.}Và yêu cầu từ bỏ nhiệm vụ hiện tại.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.49,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{These are battlefield conditions.}Để tham chiến.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:34.08,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{I'm giving you a field promotion \Nfrom genin to chunin.}Tôi sẽ thăng cấp cho cô từ genin lên chunin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.67,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,Hibi... Hibi Ranran...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:41.40,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{Your brother, Hibi Miracle, is alive.}Anh trai cô, Hibi Miracle vẫn còn sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.36,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{No one should see him like this...}Cậu cũng không muốn ai nhìn\N thấy mình lúc này nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.62,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Wait, his head's gone.}À, không có đầu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.26,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Cậu nắm thứ gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.89,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Kuro... You did it, man!}Kuro... cậu tuyệt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:16.33,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{He was able to retrieve a physiological \Nsample from a UN agent, as well.}Cậu ta đã trốn thoát thành công khỏi trụ sở UN.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.41,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{It'll be in the Ninja Lab's \Nhands soon enough.}Mau chuẩn bị tra hỏi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.66,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{I want a detailed analysis and report.}Tôi muốn thông tin phân tích và báo cáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:25.42,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{By the way, Onikobe died.}Với cả Onikobe chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:30.08,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{Kato, her direct supervisor, \Nis being put before a Ninja Tribunal.}Kato, người quản lý, đang được đưa ra toà án ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.06,Default,Taira,0,0,0,,{He's done for.}Cậu ta xong đời rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.49,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Hey, kiddo.}Này nhóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.91,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{What is this?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.96,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{U-Uh... It's about Kuro-san...}À... về Kuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:09.34,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{I know. The cops came by earlier.}Biết rồi. Lúc nãy cảnh sát có đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:13.37,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Kuro-kun's room is open. Go on in.}Phòng Kuro còn mở đó. Vào đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:14.83,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{I'll be there soon.}Tí chị cũng qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.10,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Kuro-kun!}Kuro à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.73,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Just the underwear thief...}Thằng nhóc trộm đồ lót à...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.64,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{I am not a...}Không phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.61,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Y'know, forget it.}Mà thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:33.23,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{That was one hell of an explosion!}Vụ nổ khiếp thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:37.21,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{I was in a vehicle and I still heard it.}Tôi đang trong xe còn nghe thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:42.24,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{But you guys were at a different \Nschool, right? What's up with that?}Nhưng lúc đó mấy đứa đang ở \Ntrường khác mà nhỉ? Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.87,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{I don't know if you'll believe me, but...}Không biết mọi người có tin không...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:56.76,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{So that's when I got spooked and \Nkicked the thing she threw down.}Và em hoảng sợ nên đá nó đi luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:02.39,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{And it was... Kuro-san's head, I think.}Và em nghĩ... đó là đầu của Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.91,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{His head!}Đầu á?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.89,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{I-Is that funny?}V-Vui lắm ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:10.26,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Wait. What about his funeral?}Ủa? Lễ tang cảu Kuro thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:16.15,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{I mean, I got my mourning clothes out, so...}Thì tôi đã lấy đồ tang ra rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.84,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{From what the cops told me,}Theo cảnh sát,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:22.41,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{the funeral's going to be for relatives only.}lễ tang chỉ dành cho họ hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.13,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{I see...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.16,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Feels so weird.}Cảm giác kì lạ ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:32.17,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{I saw him this morning, \Nbut by the afternoon, he's gone.}Sáng nay mới gặp cậu ta, chiều nay đã đi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:36.87,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{You're as heavy... as I figured.}Vẫn nặng như mọi khi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:41.26,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I talked to him this morning myself.}Ờ, vừa mới nói chuyện hồi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.47,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I hear you.}Hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:47.10,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Ever since I tried the stuff Ono-san's mom \Nsends him, I don't like it anymore, either.}Từ khi tôi ăn thử mấy món mẹ anh Ono\N gửi lên thì cũng chẳng muốn ăn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:54.21,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Kuro-san... You're serious \Nabout protecting me, right?}Kuro... cậu có nghiêm túc bảo vệ tớ không đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.40,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Five hundred yen a pop.}Ừm, 500 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.86,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Not a lot of good memories, actually.}Không nhiều kỉ niệm lắm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.27,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{You, too?}Cả chị nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.91,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Whatever, let's drink! \NI'm gonna have some eggplant.}Mà kệ đi! Uốn nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.97,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{What's up?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:15.93,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{U-Um, well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.55,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Are boobs, like... hard?}Ngực... có cứng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:24.37,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Look, this is embarrassing, \Nso turn the lights out.}Có hơi xấu hổ nên là tắt đèn đi nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:28.43,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Okay, close your eyes...}Rồi nhắm mắt lại đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:29.86,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.73,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Gently, now.}Nhẹ nhàng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:36.29,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Gently, like you're wrapping \Nyour hands around them.}Nhẹ nhàng và nâng niu vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.91,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{R-Right.}V-Vâng!
